definitions.definition: The first month of the Gregorian calendar , following the December of the previous year and preceding February .
examples: I hate Januarys : it's always too cold.

definitions.definition: A female given name transferred from the month name [in turn from English] .

main_definition: The first month of the Gregorian calendar , following the December of the previous year and preceding February .
secondary_definitions: ( rare ) A female given name transferred from the month name [in turn from English] .
